GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF NORTH CAROLINA
SESSION 2025
S 1
SENATE RESOLUTION 766
Sponsors: Senator Rabon (Primary Sponsor).
Referred to: Agriculture, Energy, and Environment
May 13, 2025
1 A SENATE RESOLUTION RELATING TO THE APPOINTMENT, NOMINATION, AND
2 CONFIRMATION OF D. REID WILSON AS SECRETARY OF THE DEPARTMENT OF
3 ENVIRONMENTAL QUALITY.
4 Whereas, pursuant to G.S. 143B-9(a), the Governor shall notify the President of the
5 Senate of the name of each person to be nominated as head of a principal State department; and
6 Whereas, each nomination is subject to senatorial advice and consent in conformance
7 with Section 5(8) of Article III of the North Carolina Constitution; and
8 Whereas, the Governor has appointed D. Reid Wilson as Secretary of the Department
9 of Environmental Quality pending further action by the Senate; Now, therefore,
10 Be it resolved by the Senate:
11 SECTION 1. That the Senate shall hereby consider whether to confirm D. Reid
12 Wilson as Secretary of the Department of Environmental Quality.
13 SECTION 2. This resolution is effective upon adoption.
*S766-v-1*

